{"tid":1061472,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"扑車偷60萬 哩單點睇","createTime":"2019-03-14T12:02:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-14T12:45:53.000Z","uid":221100,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cf2ede80636a11ed7ebf4a7e1132c310f01adb10","tid":1061472,"uid":221100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T12:02:36.000Z","msg":"牛頭角定安街11號對開，早上11時許，姓朱車主將其本田8人車泊在上址路邊，到附近找兄長取東西，約15分鐘後折返，驚見司機位車窗被打破，車廂滿是玻璃碎。朱放在車廂內的手提袋不翼而飛，內有16萬元現金及一隻值50萬元的勞士力鑽石名錶，損失近70萬元。警員接報到場，翻看附近商舖cctv，發現一名男子行近8人車，以磚頭掟爛司機位車窗，伸手入內偷去手提袋，再乘坐接應私家車逃去無蹤。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190314&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=59368076\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190314%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59368076&d=%2FIrJ3RR%2Fwz8SFLZOEAJhpivt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=f74d5560\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190314%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59368076&h=942369b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190314&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=59368076</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（勿跟車太貼 個阿叔堅有貨）"},{"pid":"6e73dc8d2e74276bb7ea2b0c7331b8a482d236e2","tid":1061472,"uid":27008,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T12:15:52.000Z","msg":"香港搞乜變成咁"},{"pid":"451c0a83510157c3b916cbb31734187d20db2385","tid":1061472,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T12:21:26.000Z","msg":"熟人做"},{"pid":"ad6cc9163ad8b86efef9c68403b21d07abbb3b95","tid":1061472,"uid":221100,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6e73dc8d2e74276bb7ea2b0c7331b8a482d236e2","tid":1061472,"uid":27008,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T12:15:52.000Z","msg":"香港搞乜變成咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T12:23:16.000Z","msg":"俾人踩線，冇得講，扑一吓博幾十個，大把人會，但班古惑仔人咁多分埋都唔夠7-8 個，咁就on9 啲，周到返去受成碌"},{"pid":"e3bd88e5eca7b5eb4a93f88f4d606411dc736e2b","tid":1061472,"uid":